      "text": [
        " دُهْنُ الْبَنَفْسَجِ يَرْزُنُ الدِّمَاغَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Abu Nasr, from Hammad Bin Usman, from Muhammad Bin Sowqa, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Oiling with the violet (oil) calms the brain’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "8. A number of our people have narrated from Sahl ibn Ziyad from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from ibn abu Nasr from Hammad ibn ‘Uthaman from Muhammad ibn Sawqah who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Viola oil calms down the condition of the brain/” "
        ]
      }
